                        <p>A Systematic Investment Plan (SIP) is one method of investing in tax-advantaged mutual funds. In this case, you invest a little money on a regular basis (weekly/monthly/quarterly) based on your financial situation. Simply raise your SIP donations after a certain length of time by introducing an automatic function! Step-up Top-up SIP is another name for SIP.
